{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build Your Own Digital World, Own Your Creations. MetaScapes offers four unique and immersive worlds - Sci-Fi, Cartoon, Fantasy, and Modern City. Choose your world and create your own universe. Your imagination is the limit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Metascapes empowers users to design, build, and own unique virtual worlds without the need for coding skills. MetaScapes ensures that each creation is owned by the user, granting true digital ownership to its creators.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Within MetaScapes, users can choose from four distinct and immersive themes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sci-Fi World</strong>: Explore futuristic landscapes with advanced technology and interstellar vistas.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cartoon World</strong>: Enter a vibrant and whimsical realm filled with fantastical creatures and zany architecture.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fantasy World</strong>: Step into a magical universe featuring enchanted forests, mythical beings, and grand castles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Modern World</strong>: Build a bustling urban metropolis with towering skyscrapers and sleek vehicles.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3432910?t=1739967449","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432910/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739967449","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432910/d8335a04bd6cce0ffc3fd77cb6be92a3b3fb01be/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739967449","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432910/d8335a04bd6cce0ffc3fd77cb6be92a3b3fb01be/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739967449","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"On